acc <- c()
for (tract in 1:nrow(ca_pa)) {
  if (ca_pa$STATEFP[tract] == 6) {
    if (ca_pa$COUNTYFP[tract] == 1) {
      acc <- c(acc, tract)
    }
  }
}
accmv <- c()
for (tract in acc) {
  accmv <- c(accmv, ca_pa[tract,10])
}
median(accmv)
